Round 0: dextrial wins initiative!

Round 4: mine overseer (male) takes 21 damage.

Round 5: mine overseer (male) drops 6 attack power.
Round 5: mine overseer (male) drops 6 defense.
Round 5: mine overseer (male) takes 16 damage.
Round 5: mine overseer (male) takes 18 damage.
Round 5: dextrial casts SUMMON LOVE MOSQUITO!
Round 6: mine overseer (male) takes 7 damage.
Round 6: You gain 7 hit points
Round 6: Goat Sucker plunges his tiny proboscis into your opponent, extracting 18 pints of blood, which he then squirts into your mouth. Yum, I guess.
Round 6: You gain 35 hit points
Round 6: mine overseer (male) takes 19 damage.
Round 6: dextrial attacks!
Round 7: mine overseer (male) takes 393 damage.
Round 7: You watch with glee as Goat Sucker extracts 12 drops of blood from your enemy. Then you listen with barely-concealed horror as he squirts the blood into your ear.
Round 7: You gain 23 hit points
Round 7: mine overseer (male) takes 16 damage.
Round 7: mine overseer (male) takes 21 damage.
Round 7: dextrial wins the fight!
After Battle: A love cricket plays a jaunty tune for you. You tap your feet.
